  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nFollowing from [this thread](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/issues/2888#issuecomment-1008788775), it would be nice if the VC had an opt-in flag to publish subscriptions to all backup endpoints (or maybe even *specific* endpoints :thinking:). This means that backup BNs don't need to run with subscribe-all-subnets to be reliable.\r\n\r\nI'm cautious of incurring usage on third-party nodes, that's why I suggested opt-in.\r\n",
